{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"textRadialOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[0, 4]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"symbolPlacement","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Otherwise, it is ignored.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant interleaved "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNTextAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CGVector"},{"type":"text","text":" array values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Conditional expressions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Interpolation and step functions applied to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$zoomLevel"},{"type":"text","text":" variable and\/or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature attributes"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","t